  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="heading">
        <head>Lazing On A Sunday Afternoon</head>
      </div>
      <div type="lyrics">
        <lg>
          <l>I go off to work on Monday morning</l>
          <l>Tuesday I go off to honeymoon</l>
          <l>I'll be back again before it's time for sunny-down</l>
          <l>I'll be lazing on a Sunday afternoon</l>
        </lg>
        <lg>
          <l>Bicycling on every Wednesday evening</l>
          <l>Thursday I go waltzing to the zoo</l>
          <l>I come from London town, I'm just an ordinary guy,</l>
          <l>Fridays I go painting in the Louvre</l>
        </lg>
        <lg>
          <l>I'm bound to be proposing on a Saturday night</l>
          <l>(There he goes again)</l>
          <l>I'll be lazing on a Sunday</l>
          <l>Lazing on a Sunday</l>
          <l>Lazing on a Sunday afternoon.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
